      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> beef mince</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until browned, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
